page.title: 18FARMING-TREWITHEN PART 2
page.content: {Trewithen Farm }has 2 tractors 1 Massey 65 horse power and 1 Massey 590 horse power.A 4 furrow Ransome plough. A non_cab Massey 525 combine.A Peugot pickup truck.A 150 rota spreader. A wheatly tipping trailer and a home _ made flat bottom trailer.A B47 Inter_ national bailer.A pull sledge.An old Massey finger mower.A front loader and a Quickie power loader.A transport _ box.An International corn drill.A Browns disk harrow and a Bullen drag harrow.A dorman sprayer. {John Mays concerns}are the Common Market because there might be Quotas on {sheep.
